      "span_text": "We use the Fairseq implementation for 12-layer transformer models and inherit the key hyperparameters from the Fairseq repository.  We use 2× longer learning rate linear warmup steps than in the original code repository across experiments because we observe 2× linear warmup steps can produce higher BLEU scores for both the synchronous and asynchronous runs."
